1
00:00:05,700 --> 00:00:07,500
<i>Previously on The West Wing:</i>

2
00:00:07,700 --> 00:00:09,800
You got a four-point bump.
Vinick only got two.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:14,400
When we're talking about education, we
talk about our most precious resource.

4
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:18,100
Matt Santos is a lot smarter
and tougher than you think.

5
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,600
We gotta take it to him.

6
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,300
We gotta put Santos in a jam.

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:23,500
Kazakhstan isn't China's
only oil source.

8
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:27,500
The Kazakh people are rioting because
they've been screwed out of an election.

9
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,100
Worst case, two nuclear powers
are positioning themselves to engage...

10
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:33,200
...in an armed conflict over oil.

11
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:34,500
Did the Chinese invade?

12
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:36,200
- Kazakhstan is stable.
- What is it?

13
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,800
- A nuclear accident.
- A weapon?

14
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:39,400
- A power plant.
- Is it Russia?

15
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:41,000
San Andreo, California.

16
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:42,600
They think it might blow up.

